/**
 * ModalError Component
 * 
 * A reusable component for displaying error messages in a styled container.
 * 
 * Props:
 * - `errorMessage` (string | undefined): The error message to display. If undefined or empty, nothing will render.
 * 
 * Example Usage:
 * <ModalError errorMessage="An error occurred. Please try again." />
 * 
 * Notes:
 * - Integrates with CSS Modules for styling. Ensure `Modal.module.css` is loaded.
 * - Uses CSS variables for theming: 
 *    - `--error-bg-color`: Background color of the error container.
 *    - `--error-color`: Text color of the error message.
 */
